3 reviewers (security/correctness/integration) over the contact-import
diff — no BLOCKER/HIGH. Fixes:

- Google return banner now gates on /sync res.ok (was claiming a pickable
  audience even when /sync 500'd).
- Clamp contact name to 200 chars in prepareContacts — closes the
  unbounded-name write on the token-authed phone path (all paths covered).
- QR/import token TTL 10->5 min + honest doc on within-TTL replay.
- parse-vcard strips a mailto: scheme (iCloud exports) so addresses don't
  hard-bounce.
- emailDomain strips a trailing dot so gmail.com. can't evade the filter.
- QR generated at 176px to match its render size.

+3 regression tests (name-clamp, mailto, trailing-dot). 407 email tests
pass, tsc 0, eslint clean, next build compiles + typechecks.

